// public.learning_modules / public.learning_module_competencies /
// public.learning_records created by supabase/migrations/0005_add_learning.sql.
// Following the cross-module convention (scorecards / performance / compensation):
// cross-entity references (competencies, employees, users, appraisals) are FKs in
